.IX Item "val_rc_status"
Validation status for a given RRset.  This can be one of the following:
.Sp
.Vb 2
\&    VAL_SUCCESS
\&        Answer received and validated successfully.
.Ve
.Sp
.Vb 5
\&    VAL_NONEXISTENT_NAME
\&        No name was present and a valid proof of non-
